descriptionHtml:
I take no responsibility on making this mod the guy who made the mod got banned and that was the day the mod was released when I made a video on it. BOB666 was the person who made this mod.

To get this mod you have to right help wings and then player.placeatme and then the number at the start of the line.

INSTALLATION:
To install this mod you will need to use console commands the button to get the console commands up it the one left to 1, above TAB and below ESC. Then type (help wings) without brackets and all of these words should come up. You can scroll through them by the PAGEUP and PAGEDOWN button on your computer. These are.

ARMO: (51001838) \'Darkangel Wings\'
ARMO; (51001837) \'Darkseraph Wings\'
ARMO: (51001836) \'Angelwings\'
ARMO: (51001835) \'Demon Wings\'
ARMO: (51001834) \'Bloodangel Wings\'
ARMO: (5100182E) \'Bloodseraph Wings\'
ARMO: (510012C9) \'Seraph Demon Wings\'
ARMO: (51000D62) \'Seraph Wings\'

Then find the one you want and then write either player.placeatme or player.additem and the number that is in brackets.
eg. player.placeatme 51000D62
Then the wings you wanted will be placed at your feet. Also you can put a number a the end of it for how many of the wings you want.
author: KILLZAMOI
